                  </persName>
            . I am the officer. I took the prisoner.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>

               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182802210088"></xptr>Prisoner's Defence. I saw the shoes laying under the window - I took them up, and put them into my apron; when I saw the man coming after me I ran.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 17.</p>
